        "text": "# \ud83d\udfe2 HEARTBEAT_WAKEUP\nYou have been routed ONE isolated task. \n*Task ID*: EPIC-DFP-MOD-data-store\n*Module*: data-store\n*Workdir*: /home/ienliven/Projects/sdlc-factory/workspace/EPIC-DFP-MOD-data-store\n*Phase*: QA_REVIEW\n\n## SYSTEM CONTEXT\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"module_id\": \"data-store\",\n  \"regression_context\": \"No active regression reported.\",\n  \"structural_context\": \"## > BEGIN_ENVIRONMENT\\nStack: Docker Compose, React/Vite (pnpm), Python (uv), PostgreSQL\\nEntry_Point: http://localhost:8000\\nInterface_Mount_Selector: #root\\nINTEGRATION_TEST_CMD: cd ui-gateway && pnpm install && npx playwright install chromium && CI=true npx playwright test --reporter=list\\n## > END_ENVIRONMENT\\n\\n## > BEGIN_MODULE: data-store\\nType: LEAF\\nDescription: The PostgreSQL persistence layer.\\nResponsibilities:\\n- Provide a PostgreSQL database initialization script (e.g., `init.sql`) to create the necessary tables for caching daily adjusted market closes for funds and benchmarks.\\n- Must be isolated on an internal Docker network, unreachable from the host machine.\\n- Data persisted via Docker volumes.\\n## > END_MODULE: data-store\",\n  \"semantic_context\": \"### File: test.py\\n```\\nhello factory\\n```\\n\\n### File: test.py\\n```\\nhello factory\\n```\",\n  \"memory_insights\": \"No historic pgvector insights found for tester.\"\n}\n```\n\nThe SDLC Protocol and your Playbook are your core instructions.\nCRITICAL: If successful, your handoff JSON must strictly validate against this schema:\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"required\": [\n    \"status\",\n    \"phase_completed\",\n    \"module_id\",\n    \"all_tests_passed\"\n  ],\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"status\": {\n      \"const\": \"success\"\n    },\n    \"phase_completed\": {\n      \"const\": \"QA_REVIEW\"\n    },\n    \"module_id\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\"\n    },\n    \"all_tests_passed\": {\n      \"const\": true\n    },\n    \"fai